248
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:33,100
Ada lagi?

249
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,660
Tidak ada yang lain.

250
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:36,830
Pikirkan lagi.

251
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,220
Tidak peduli seberapa banyak aku berpikir,
tidak ada yang lain, Hongbing.

252
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:40,660
Hongbing.

253
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,110
Saya meminta Anda melakukannya
tes urin terakhir kali.

254
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,290
Anda melakukannya, kan?

255
00:11:44,290 --> 00:11:45,140
Ya.

256
00:11:45,380 --> 00:11:46,220
Baiklah kalau begitu.

257
00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:47,660
Datang.

258
00:11:47,660 --> 00:11:50,310
Setelah kita selesai makan ini,
kembalilah ke stasiun bersamaku.

259
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:52,340
Hal pertama besok pagi,
bawa aku ke tambang

260
00:11:52,340 --> 00:11:53,180
untuk menemukan Ma Heping.

261
00:11:54,820 --> 00:11:55,660
Minum habis.

262
00:12:05,860 --> 00:12:06,700
Hongbing,

263
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:09,750
