291
00:13:18,460 --> 00:13:19,870
Tidak perlu turun ke poros hari ini.

292
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:21,710
Ayo berkumpul.

293
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:23,740
Kemarilah.
Tuan Huang ingin mengatakan sesuatu.

294
00:13:23,740 --> 00:13:24,580
Ayo cepat.

295
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:26,540
Semuanya, di sini.

296
00:13:27,220 --> 00:13:28,780
Letakkan apa pun yang Anda pegang.

297
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:31,460
Dengarkan aku.

298
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:33,740
Pertama-tama, saya sudah mengecewakan kalian semua.

299
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:35,340
Mulai hari ini,

300
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:37,040
